All Implemented Interfaces:
com.trolltech.qt.gui.QPaintDeviceInterface, com.trolltech.qt.QtJambiInterface
public class PartTileBrowser
extends com.trolltech.qt.gui.QMainWindow

This class is an example of how RapidSmith could be used to build interactive tools using Qt or other GUI packages. This class creates a zoom-able 2D array of the tiles found in the devices installed with RapidSmith. This example requires the Qt Jambi (Qt for Java) jars to run.

Author:
marc
